    Scope and Contents
Taylor, a retired teacher and principal, discusses his experiences in education: high school and college education in Lincoln, Illinois and at Illinois State University, teaching in Lincoln, supplies and books, students, teachers and staff, discipline, becoming a principal, working at two different schools, teaching techniques, changes in schools and programs, accomplishments and failures in education. 4 tapes, 265 mins. 
Interview by Steve Sauer, 1991 
